# Vehicle Inheritance Project

This Java project demonstrates inheritance using a Vehicle parent class and multiple child classes.

## Classes
- Vehicle
- Moped
- Car
- SemiTruck
- Hovercraft

## Concepts Used
- Inheritance
- Constructors
- super()
- Getters and Setters
- Object Creation

## How It Works
The Vehicle class contains shared properties like:
- color
- number of passengers
- cargo capacity
- fuel capacity

Child classes inherit these properties and use constructors with super() to initialize them.

